    "description": "WingArc1st Inc. develops and sells software and services in Japan. The company offers SVF comprehensive form platform that comprises Form Design, which defines the layout of forms and creates form files; Interface, which connects host systems and the output engine that acts as the main body of SVF; and Form Output, which is the engine that combines form definitions and analyzed data to output forms. It also provides SCF Cloud, a cloud form service; document management platforms, including invoiceAgent documents document management solution and invoiceAgent AI OCR form digitization solution; and Dr.Sum, a database engine to optimize integration and aggregation of data. In addition, the company offers MotionBoard, a BI Dashboard for business managers and users to accelerate business performance; and VyNDEX, an app for salesforce to increase CRM adoption. WingArc1st Inc. was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
